<br />

<br />
After 5 years of playing I still like to sit in places like Neriak and look at the cool neon signs while I drink beer in real life and watch tv.... or in the swamps of Innathule or No Hope and listen to the ambience of the creatures.
<br />

<br />
As long as they have a massive, detailed world in which I can feel totally immersed in, I will definatly play EQII. If they concentrate on flashy graphics and voice-overs (LAME!) to the detriment of content and playability, they will get only a month's subscription outta me.
